    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Consultation on next steps for more environmentally friendly haulage
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Government launches 2 consultations following successful trial of longer semi-trailers, which have been shown to cut emissions and boost haulier productivity.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 9 November 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 10 November 2020
      — <a href="#history" class="app-c-published-dates__history-link govuk-link">see all updates</a>
</div>

